entries.femaleVariant: [Knock once]
OK. Come inside, quick.
Hanako-sama! V is living proof of the terrible crime your brother committed!
We can confirm every word she speaks if only you will help her with the Relic.
entries.maleVariant: We can confirm every word he speaks if only you will help him with the Relic.

entries.femaleVariant: Hanako-sama?
[Sit] I was there when Saburo died.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ハナコ様… 彼女が例の人物です" t="Hanako-sama... This is the woman I spoke of." b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="ハナコ様… 彼が例の人物です" t="Hanako-sama... This is the man I spoke of." b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: You must be mad to think I will listen to such nonsense.
Got nothing to lose. I'm dyin'.
I am insane – thanks to your Relic.
Hard to believe, I know. But I wanna make you an offer.
Thing is, I'm damned determined and got nothin' to lose.
"Mad?" Got no idea, lady.
Look, I know it's a lot to take in, let alone believe.
Lost your fuckin' mind?!
There is no time to explain. We must meet.
I feared they had caught you.
Yeah... for now!
An abandoned apartment block on Vine Street. Second floor, number three-zero-three.
V? Are you secure?
Hurry!
Gonna tell me what the fuck you were thinking?
Why? My word mean shit to you?
Hanako-sama, I apologize on her behalf...
entries.maleVariant: Hanako-sama, I apologize on his behalf...

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, shut up, Goro! Was s'posed to be honest. Well, that's what I'm bein'!
Fine, maybe I am just a two-bit thief... but I'm the two-bit thief that stole that fuckin' Relic off you.
Slotted it in, took a bullet to the brain, died…
So I got exactly nothin' to lose. But you got lots.
Oh yeah. And now I'm stuck with Johnny fuckin' Silverhand in there, and I'll do anything to get him out.
entries.maleVariant: Oh yeah. And now I got Johnny fuckin' Silverhand in there, and I'll do anything to get him out.

entries.femaleVariant: You... died?
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="どうか話を聞いてあげてください" t="Please, listen to what she has to say." b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="どうか話を聞いてあげてください" t="Please, listen to what he has to say." b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: Got your prototype Relic jammed in my head.
entries.maleVariant: I got your prototype Relic jammed in my head.

entries.femaleVariant: By freak coincidence it stopped, then helped me survive, a bullet. Now it's slowly killin' me.
entries.maleVariant: By freak coincidence it stopped, then helped me survive, a bullet. But now, it's slowly killin' me.

entries.femaleVariant: One of your personality engrams is overwriting itself onto my psyche, and if I don't find a way to stop it... well, it won't end well for me.
[Sit] Your brother is the real murderer.
I'm sorry to be speaking to you under these circumstances.
I was there that night at Konpeki Plaza. I saw Saburo Arasaka die.
I'm sorry that we have to speak under such... circumstances.
Yorinobu's the murderer.
Now're you gonna tell me what the fuck you were thinkin'?!
All Arasaka's looking for us.
Right about now, Hanako's the most famous missing person in the world…
I am aware.
So every Arasaka soldier is on our trail.
You are right. Let us not waste any time.
Come.
Tell her the truth about Yorinobu, no embellishment. And state your terms clearly.
She tried to enable her tracker.
I had no choice.
That is the second time today I have heard that.
Also know you're an honorable person, worthy of trust. And that's why I wanna make you an offer.
You? Make me an offer?
The Relic your brother tried to hawk off to NetWatch is in my head. Right now.
Took a bullet to the brain, but the tech on the chip saved me. Now it's slowly killin' me.
One of your personality constructs, engrams, it's overwriting my psyche.
Gotta stop the process before it's too late. Know you got the means to help me.
entries.maleVariant: Gotta stop the process before it's too late. I know you got the means to help me.

entries.femaleVariant: See, I got a voice in my head. An engram, one of your personality constructs.
entries.maleVariant: Got a voice in my head, see? An engram, one of your personality constructs.

entries.femaleVariant: Engram?
Yeah. I stole the Relic Yorinobu tried to peddle off on NetWatch.
He strangled your father. I saw it with my own eyes.
Perhaps to you she will listen.
He wasn't poisoned. That's a lie your brother made up and spread.
While I was makin' my escape, got a bullet to the brain... Relic saved me.
entries.maleVariant: While I was makin' my escape, I got a bullet to the brain... Relic saved me.

entries.femaleVariant: Now the damn thing's killin' me. And I gotta stop it.
entries.maleVariant: But now the damn thing's killin' me. And I gotta stop it.

entries.femaleVariant: I offered her some tea...
You kidnap Hanako Arasaka and offer her a cup of fuckin' tea?!
Yes... She respectfully declined.
Yorinobu is the murderer.
My word means nothing to you?
Argh... Not now!
Last chance to get the fuck outta here!
Forget him, guy's toast! 'Less you wanna wind up like him!
Keep low and eyes three-sixty! They're in the hallway!
The fuck you doin'? You lost it?! He's beyond any sort of help!
Takemura! Can't leave him back there!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="うおおおおお！" t="Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha!" b="" a=""/>
You should not have returned! You will die here with me!
Thank me later! Need to find a way out now – fast!
Arasaka – they have found us!
Did you hear that?
Go and check.
Ruuuuun!
[Stand]
Well?
Go.
Are you mad? Wait!
[Check hallway]
Got a bad feeling about this…
entries.maleVariant: I got a bad feelin' about this…

entries.femaleVariant: Dammit!
Where are you?
There are empty rooms to the right! It's our only chance!
[Knock three times]
[Knock four times]
Knock four times!
Oh shit...
Be careful!
V, stay with me!
Oof... What the...
Don't you fuckin' dare float off! Not now!
C'mon! Gotta get the fuck outta the city!
Secure the room!
Yes, sir!
Sector's clear!
The hell it is! Sweep it again!
[Stand]
[Knock again]
I used a sedative.
On the ground, cunt! Don't move!
entries.maleVariant: On the ground, asshole! Don't move!

entries.femaleVariant: We must go different ways! Alone we have a better chance!
Really?! Think so?!
Then go! Now!
